
Sentiment Analysis Tool: Develop a tool that can analyze sentiments from social media posts, reviews, or comments. This can be useful for businesses to understand customer opinions about their products or services.

Chatbot Development: Create a chatbot that can understand and respond to natural language inputs, providing customer service, answering FAQs, or even offering personalized recommendations.

Text Classification: Develop a system that can categorize text into predefined classes. This could be used for spam detection, news categorization, or even medical diagnosis based on patient symptoms descriptions.

Text Summarization - develop a system that can automatically generate a concise and meaningful summary of a given text.
